###  http://www.semanticweb.org/filippos/ontologies/2023/4/NCREM_Ontology#Schedule
ncrem:Schedule rdf:type owl:Class ;
               skos:definition "A time-based control logic or pattern for operating building systems or components." .


###  http://www.semanticweb.org/filippos/ontologies/2023/4/NCREM_Ontology#Season
ncrem:Season rdf:type owl:Class ;
             rdfs:subClassOf ncrem:Time ;
             skos:definition "A temporal classification (e.g., winter, summer) used to define seasonal variations in environmental or operational conditions." .


###  http://www.semanticweb.org/filippos/ontologies/2023/4/NCREM_Ontology#Self_Consumption_Ratio
