ncrem:Time rdf:type owl:Class ;
           rdfs:subClassOf core:Property ;
           skos:definition "A temporal concept used to define sequences, durations, intervals, or timestamps associated with system operations or environmental conditions." .


###  http://www.semanticweb.org/filippos/ontologies/2023/4/NCREM_Ontology#Transmission
ncrem:Transmission rdf:type owl:Class ;
                   rdfs:subClassOf ncrem:Material_Property ;
