###  http://www.semanticweb.org/filippos/ontologies/2023/4/NCREM_Ontology#Weight
ncrem:Weight rdf:type owl:Class ;
             rdfs:subClassOf ncrem:Material_Property ;
             skos:definition "The measure of the gravitational force acting on an object or material, often relevant for structural load calculations." .


###  http://www.semanticweb.org/filippos/ontologies/2023/4/NCREM_Ontology#Workflow
ncrem:Workflow rdf:type owl:Class ;
               skos:definition "A sequence of tasks or operations performed to complete a process, typically defined by temporal order or dependencies." .


###  http://www.semanticweb.org/filippos/ontologies/2023/4/NCREM_Ontology#Zone_Cooling_Setpoint
