###  http://www.semanticweb.org/filippos/ontologies/2023/4/NCREM_Ontology#Zone_Temperature
ncrem:Zone_Temperature rdf:type owl:Class ;
                       rdfs:subClassOf core:Temperature ;
                       skos:definition "The air temperature measured or estimated in a specific zone, often used for HVAC control or comfort analysis." .


###  http://www.semanticweb.org/filippos/ontologies/2023/4/NCREM_Ontology#Zone_Transmitted_Energy
