ncrem:Accumulated_Charged_Energy_from_System skos:definition "The total amount of energy cumulatively charged into an energy storage system over a period of time."@en .
ncrem:Accumulated_Discharged_Energy_from_System skos:definition "The total amount of energy cumulatively discharged from an energy storage system over a period of time."@en .
ncrem:Accumulated_PV_Electricity_Production skos:definition "The cumulative electricity generated by a photovoltaic system over a defined time period."@en .
ncrem:AirPollutantsOperationalStage skos:definition "A KPI describing air-pollutant impacts associated with the operational stage of a building or neighborhood."@en .
ncrem:CO2 skos:definition "A KPI or property related to carbon dioxide concentration or emissions, depending on the measurement context."@en .
ncrem:CO2EmissionsOperationalStage skos:definition "A KPI describing carbon dioxide emissions associated with the operational stage of a building or neighborhood."@en .
ncrem:Comfort_KPIs skos:definition "A category of key performance indicators used to evaluate occupant comfort conditions."@en .
ncrem:Data skos:definition "A generic information artifact used as input, output, or reference in the NCREM domain."@en .
ncrem:EV_Charging_Power skos:definition "The electrical power used while charging an electric vehicle."@en .
ncrem:EV_Energy_Consumption skos:definition "The amount of energy consumed by an electric vehicle or charging process."@en .
ncrem:Electricity_Power_Consumption skos:definition "The rate at which electrical power is consumed by a system, device, or process."@en .
ncrem:Energy_KPIs skos:definition "A category of key performance indicators used to evaluate energy-related performance."@en .
ncrem:Monthly_Electricity_Consumption skos:definition "The amount of electricity consumed over a monthly period."@en .
ncrem:OperationalCostOfEnergy skos:definition "A KPI representing the cost of energy during the operational stage of a building or neighborhood."@en .
ncrem:PV_Power skos:definition "The electrical power produced by a photovoltaic system at a given time."@en .
ncrem:Power_Consumption_in_Charging_Mode skos:definition "The electrical power consumed while a storage or vehicle system is operating in charging mode."@en .
ncrem:Power_Consumption_in_Discharging_Mode skos:definition "The electrical power consumed while a storage or vehicle system is operating in discharging mode."@en .
ncrem:Solar_Irradiance skos:definition "The power of solar radiation received on a surface per unit area."@en .

